Sentencas: (La0.8Sr0.2)(0.98)MnO3-8-Zr0.92Y0.16O2-8 (YSZ) has been widely studied as the cathode for solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs), but its low activity has been a cell performance limiting factor.
